# PHP: Convert title to slug
```php
<?php
function slug( $text )
	{
		$trans = [
			'Ð°' => 'a', 'Ð±' => 'b', 'Ð²' => 'v', 'Ð³' => 'g', 'Ð´' => 'd', 'Ðµ' => 'e', 'Ñ' => 'jo', 'Ð¶' => 'zh', 'Ð·' => 'z', 'Ð¸' => 'i', 'Ð¹' => 'jj',
			'Ðº' => 'k', 'Ð»' => 'l', 'Ð¼' => 'm', 'Ð½' => 'n', 'Ð¾' => 'o', 'Ð¿' => 'p', 'Ñ' => 'r', 'Ñ' => 's', 'Ñ' => 't', 'Ñ' => 'u', 'Ñ' => 'f',
			'Ñ' => 'kh', 'Ñ' => 'c', 'Ñ' => 'ch', 'Ñ' => 'sh', 'Ñ' => 'shh', 'Ñ' => '', 'Ñ' => 'y', 'Ñ' => '', 'Ñ' => 'eh', 'Ñ' => 'ju', 'Ñ' => 'ja',
		];
		$text  = mb_strtolower( $text, 'UTF-8' ); // lowercase cyrillic letters too
		$text  = strtr( $text, $trans ); // transliterate cyrillic letters
		$text  = preg_replace( '/[^A-Za-z0-9 _.]/', '', $text );
		$text  = preg_replace( '/[ _.]+/', '-', trim( $text ) );
		$text  = trim( $text, '-' );
		return $text;
	}
```
# JS: Convert title to slug
PHP `strtr` function alternative in JavaScript.
We add this function as part of `jQuery`.

```js
jQuery.strtr=function(str, from, to)
{
	var fr='', i=0, j=0, lenStr=0, lenFrom=0, tmpStrictForIn=false, fromTypeStr='', toTypeStr='', istr='';
	var tmpFrom=[];
	var tmpTo=[];
	var ret='';
	var match=false;

	// Received replace_pairs?
	// Convert to normal from->to chars
	if(typeof from==='object')
	{
		for(fr in from)
			if(from.hasOwnProperty(fr))
			{
				tmpFrom.push(fr);
				tmpTo.push(from[fr]);
			}

		from=tmpFrom;
		to=tmpTo;
	}

	// Walk through subject and replace chars when needed
	lenStr=str.length;
	lenFrom=from.length;
	fromTypeStr=typeof from==='string';
	toTypeStr=typeof to==='string';

	for(i=0; i<lenStr; i++)
	{
		match=false;
		if(fromTypeStr)
		{
			istr=str.charAt(i);
			for(j=0; j<lenFrom; j++)
				if(istr==from.charAt(j))
				{
					match=true;
					break;
				}
		}
		else
			for(j=0; j<lenFrom; j++)
				if(str.substr(i, from[j].length)==from[j])
				{
					match=true;
					// Fast forward
					i=(i+from[j].length)-1;
					break;
				}
		if(match) ret+=toTypeStr ? to.charAt(j) : to[j];
		else ret+=str.charAt(i);
	}

	return ret;
}
```

Actual function to convert text into slug.
Again we impelement it as `jQuery`'s method.

