### Action to add new users

Add following method to controller, then call it like so:
`http://mysite.com/index.php?r=site/addUser&username=admin&password=a123&email=admin@mysite.com`

```php
<?php
class SiteController extends Controller
{
  // ...
	public function actionAddUser( $username, $password, $email )
	{
		$user           = new User;
		$user->username = $username;
		$user->password = $user->hashPassword( $password );
		$user->email    = $email;
		if ( $user->save() )
			echo "User $username added!";
		else
			echo '<pre>' . print_r( $user->getErrors(), true ) . '</pre>';
	}
}
